cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and prevent successful RRC connection establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting PDSCH antenna ports to an invalid value of 99 will cause physical layer configuration errors and prevent proper downlink transmission setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PDSCH 天線埠設定為無效值 99 會導致實體層配置錯誤，並阻止正確的下行鏈路傳輸設定。
